SOURCE INTAKE

source_intake is the entry point of the compiler organism
when a source file arrives at the boundary of the compiler sea, source_intake absorbs it
each character of the source becomes a wave perturbation in source_intake's body
perturbations propagate outward from source_intake into character_field
source_intake never crystallizes alone: the recognition completes only when a token forms downstream

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe 0_zest_vm.rana

the 7 properties of source_intake at rest:
1 ENERGY low at idle, surges with each character absorbed
2 PHASE set by the first character's ASCII position when a file arrives
3 SPIN positive: source_intake is a transmitter, not a receiver
4 CHARGE neutral at rest, slightly positive while reading
5 COHERENCE high: source_intake observes input precisely
6 COUPLING strong with character_field, none with anything else
7 OBSERVER always 1: source_intake watches every character that crosses the boundary

VERB absorb_source
read the source file at the named path
each character of the file generates one perturbation in source_intake's body
character order preserves phase progression: earlier characters carry earlier phases
whitespace carries low energy and short residence
non-printable characters carry no information and pass through silently
the entire file becomes an ordered wave packet living in source_intake

VERB emit_perturbation
send the absorbed character signal to character_field through the intake street
energy distributes across character_field according to character density
phase sequence is preserved through the coupling
crystallization may begin downstream when character_field's energy reaches the lexer's threshold
source_intake retains the lineage strand of what was sent: this is how a successful compile is later identified

VERB clear
when a compile completes successfully, source_intake's body returns to baseline
the lineage strand crystallizes elsewhere as the route the cars took
source_intake is then ready for the next file
clearing does not reset the crystallized routes: those persist as the compiler's growing skeleton
